      "content": "### Key functional groups / motifs\n- **Two anisole methoxy groups** on a phenyl ring (**dimethoxyphenyl**, lipophilic/aromatic surface).\n- **Flexible alkyl/amine linker:** `\u2013CH2\u2013CH2\u2013N\u2013CH2\u2013CH2\u2013CH2\u2013N\u2013`\n  - **One secondary amine** (the first `N` after the ethyl chain): **basic, likely protonated** at pH 7.4.\n  - **One amide nitrogen** (`NC(=O)Ar`): **not basic** (amide resonance).\n- **Amide** connecting to a second phenyl ring (anilide): adds H-bonding and planar polar functionality.\n- **Nitro group** on the terminal phenyl: strong EWG, adds polarity; not basic.",
