      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "### Structural alerts relevant to hERG\n- **Classic hERG pharmacophore pattern present:** **(cationic amine) + (two hydrophobic/aromatic regions) + (flexible spacer)**.\n- Not a piperidine/terfenadine per se, but **terfenadine-like topology** (aryl\u2013spacer\u2013basic center\u2013spacer\u2013aryl/amide).",
